    <item>
      <title>HOBO BN MCP v1.1.0 released</title>
      <link>/blog/2026-04-16-hobo-bn-mcp-1-1-0/-index/</link>
      <pubDate>Thu, 16 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>/blog/2026-04-16-hobo-bn-mcp-1-1-0/-index/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;I was too stingy to pay 💰💰💰 for a commercial Binary Ninja license and a pile of tokens that MCP waste every time I say &lt;em&gt;&amp;ldquo;hello! how are you?&amp;rdquo;&lt;/em&gt; to Claude. So I wrote my own MCP-like solution from scratch.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Key features:&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Any HTTP client.&lt;/strong&gt; Works with &lt;code&gt;curl&lt;/code&gt;, Python scripts, browsers, Postman, LLM agents — anything that speaks HTTP.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Any Binary Ninja license.&lt;/strong&gt; No headless ($1499+) license required.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Zero dependencies.&lt;/strong&gt; One &lt;code&gt;.py&lt;/code&gt; file, no &lt;code&gt;pip install&lt;/code&gt; required.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Read + comment.&lt;/strong&gt; Full read access to Binary Ninja&amp;rsquo;s analysis, plus the ability to set comments.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Meet &lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/altvist/hobo-bn-mcp&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;&#xA;    HOBO BN MCP v1.1.0&lt;span class=&#34;tail&#34;&gt;&lt;svg viewBox=&#34;0 0 24 24&#34; width=&#34;0.85em&#34; height=&#34;0.85em&#34; class=&#34;external-link-icon&#34; fill=&#34;none&#34; xmlns=&#34;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#34;&gt;&#xA;        &lt;g stroke-width=&#34;0&#34;&gt;&lt;/g&gt;&lt;g stroke-linecap=&#34;round&#34; stroke-linejoin=&#34;round&#34;&gt;&lt;/g&gt;&#xA;        &lt;g&gt;&#xA;            &lt;path d=&#34;M10 4H6C4.89543 4 4 4.89543 4 6V18C4 19.1046 4.89543 20 6 20H18C19.1046 20 20 19.1046 20 18V14M11 13L20 4M20 4V9M20 4H15&#34; stroke=&#34;currentColor&#34; stroke-width=&#34;2&#34; stroke-linecap=&#34;round&#34; stroke-linejoin=&#34;round&#34;&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&#xA;        &lt;/g&gt;&#xA;    &lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;!&lt;/p&gt;</description>
